{
  "stem": "21817.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had small-- made out almost of plywood, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were sleeping about eight, 10 kids in one place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had supervision.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My older one attended, but not the younger one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My older sister, which was almost nine or 10 years old, approximately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the camp?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Dina.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the older one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shasna was the, the youngest one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no name of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would just go to Jewish camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Camp out of the city, that's all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was organized by the-- the rabbi that was over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, we had a rabbi from cheder, and he supervised us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a teacher, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Young man, very progressive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was at home, and early in the morning we had a horrible explosion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- this I'll never forget-- it was September 1st.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "An artillery bomb exploded a few hundred yards from our house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was out-- then we saw the Polish soldiers going closer to the border, going up north.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was the major thoroughfare, so they used to-- they used to go over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we realized, from mouth to mouth, that the Germans invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they built the fortification before the war-- so the Germans didn't-- was not-- didn't come into Mlawa first.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were almost close to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were encircled, but they came from the other side, instead of breaking through, or go straight ahead.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They came from other side.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were close to Warsaw and then they come back to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then we saw troops are coming in from the opposite side, not from the German border.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
